metadata.name: The forest
metadata.description: The dark and dense forest holds ancient and mysterious secrets. Wild animals shun the area, but brave adventurers say there are untold treasures hidden in the forest trails. Some say that there is an ancient temple hidden among the trees, while others claim that there are monstrous creatures that inhabit the forest. No one knows the truth, but everyone agrees that it's best to avoid it. Are you willing to risk it all in pursuit of the unknown?
